Recent years have seen an increased perception of a lack of progress in the war on cancer, and renewed motivation to confront the disease.<ref name=Hughes2006 /><ref>{{cite web
| url=http://health.usnews.com/articles/health/cancer/2008/06/12/we-need-a-new-war-on-cancer.html
