| publisher=[[U.S. News and World Report]]
| accessdate=2009-10-26
}}</ref>
On July 15, 2008, the [[United States Senate Committee on Health, Education, Labor, and Pensions]] convened a panel discussion titled, ''Cancer: Challenges and Opportunities in the 21st Century''.<ref>{{cite web
| url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9YicA5ANMdE
