The LAF encourages similar commitments from other nations to combat the disease. 

Livestrong Day is an annual event established by the LAF to serve as "a global day of action to raise awareness about the fight against cancer." Individuals from around the world are encouraged to host cancer-oriented events in their local communities and then register their events with the LAF website.<ref>{{cite web
| url=http://www.livestrongaction.org/map
| title=LIVESTRONG Day home page
