The sequence information provides a comprehensive catalog of approximately 90% of the [[somatic]] mutations in the cancerous tissue, providing a more detailed molecular and genetic understanding of cancer biology than was previously possible, and offering hope for the development of new therapeutic strategies gleaned from these insights.<ref>{{cite news
